headline.print_headline: Milwaukee Police Fire Officer Who Shot Man in Park
headline.main: Milwaukee Police Fire Officer Who Shot Man in Park

lead_paragraph: Milwaukee Police Chief Edward Flynn has fired an officer who he said instigated a fight with a mentally ill man that eventually led the officer to shoot the man 14 times, killing him.
